Package: go-socks5
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libc6 (>= 2.17), ca-certificates
Description: SOCKS5 proxy server with authentication and traffic accounting
 A SOCKS5 proxy server written in Go with local SQLite and remote API
 support for authentication and traffic accounting.
 .
 Features include:
  * RFC 1928 compliant SOCKS5 CONNECT command
  * Local SQLite database or remote API validation
  * Traffic accounting to local SQLite or remote API
  * Flexible modes: local-only, remote-only, or both
  * Mock mode for testing without real backends